      "imagery": "The site's visual language is almost entirely UI-driven, with minimal decorative graphics. When present, images are limited to small, functional icons. These icons are typically outlined or filled in #1c2024 (Midnight Ink) or #60646c (Cool Gray), maintaining a functional, monochrome aesthetic. There is no photography or complex illustration, reinforcing the technical and content-focused nature of the brand. Imagery plays a supporting, explanatory role, never decorative or atmospheric, ensuring content takes center stage.",
